  "notes": "Hand-tuned exemplar for Security compliance (LAS1-LAS8). Argus persona — zero-trust mindset. Required sections include all five primary security-relevant docs. mTLS/encryption keywords carry maximum weight. plaintext_secret_present is a present-pattern anti-marker that triggers a blocker gap if literal credentials appear in any candidate file."
